        "subject": "LU-19644 tests: skip sanity/150ib for older clients",
        "message": "LU-19644 tests: skip sanity/150ib for older clients\n\nSkip sanity test_150ib for older clients because they calculate\nthe wrong blocks count for an ldiskfs MDT with extents enabled.\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial\nTest-Parameters: testlist=sanity env=ONLY=150,HONOR_EXCEPT=true clientversion=2.17\nFixes: 2cbe29c282 (\"LU-19644 tests: fix blocks math in sanity/150ib\")\nFixes: f57455ffa2 (\"LU-17055 ldiskfs: add falloc(zero) for OST/ext\")\nSigned-off-by: Andreas Dilger <adilger@thelustrecollective.com>\nChange-Id: I9417bd66ce50109b7023e0d3654ff79294235ec7\n"
      },
